Hi there again!

Here is my second Wallpaper Collection of Skyrim (31 images).
This one is a little bit \"darker\" than the first one! Also, i\'ve added fog to the black bars.

Hope you like it!

@wasienka: Rift and Blackreach Shots are inside, too :)
